### Crear usuario (solo ADMIN, uso administrativo)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "username": "john",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "roles": ["USER"],
  "isActive": true
}

### Listar usuarios (paginado) - solo ADMIN
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Buscar usuarios por texto (username o email) - solo ADMIN
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10&search=john
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Obtener usuario por id - solo ADMIN
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Actualizar usuario (dueño o ADMIN) - ejemplo completo con avatar y bio
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "username": "john_updated",
  "email": "john_updated@example.com",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "isActive": true,
  "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/avatars/john.png",
  "bio": "Jugador tryhard de ranked y fan de los RPG"
}

### Actualizar solo avatar y bio (dueño o ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/avatars/john_v2.png",
  "bio": "Ahora también juego indies raros"
}

### Actualizar roles de un usuario (solo ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "roles": ["ADMIN"]
}

### Desactivar usuario (dueño o ADMIN si actualiza su propio isActive, o ADMIN si lo usa como gestión)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "isActive": false
}

### Eliminar usuario (solo ADMIN)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Ver perfil público de un usuario (sin auth, sólo datos de perfil y stats)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile/1
Content-Type: application/json
